1. Install Rails Engines Plugin

ruby script/plugin discover
ruby script/plugin install engines

or

ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/lazyatom/engines.git

2. Install SurveyOR

ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/breakpointer/surveyor.git

3. Setup SurveyOR

Add to config/environment.rb above after require File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), 'boot'): require File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), '../vendor/plugins/engines/boot')



Add to config/routes.rb: map.from_plugin :surveyor
 
Run: script/generate plugin_migration && rake db:migrate